OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRain in the northwest will
OL,6,Fspread southeast across all parts this
OL,7,Fmorning. Drier weather with scattered
OL,8,Fshowers following on behind this
OL,9,Fafternoon, turning wintry on hills.
OL,10,FMild at first in the east, otherwise
OL,11,Fturning colder this afternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA few showers this evening.
OL,14,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,15,Fmainly dry with clear periods and just
OL,16,Fthe odd shower. Cold with frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
