OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FMainly dry in the morning.
OL,6,FOutbreaks of rain and high ground snow
OL,7,Fspreading east during the afternoon
OL,8,Fand evening. Becoming drier for a time
OL,9,Fin the northwest in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FRain,
OL,12,Fhill snow clearing east on Friday
OL,13,Fmorning, otherwise cloudy with
OL,14,Fshowers, wintry on hills. Rain and
OL,15,Fhill snow spreading northeast on
OL,16,FSaturday. Wintry showers on Sunday.
OL,17,FWindy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
